8 POLICY COMMITTEE RECOMMENDATION
9 An Act relating to public corruption; amending 21
O.S. 2021, Section 344, which relates to crimes
10 against state revenue; changing punishment; providing
for removal; adding new law 21 O.S. Section 365,
11 which relates to nonpublic government information;
stating elements of certain unlawful acts; providing
12 penalties; amending 22 O.S. 2021, Sections 1181,
1181.1, and 1181.2, which relate to removal;
13 providing definitions; specifying scope; adding new
laws 74 O.S. Sections 85.22A, 85.22B, and 85.22C,
14 which relate to collusion and conflicts of interest;
stating elements of certain unlawful acts; requiring
15 certain disclosures for bidders; amending 74 O.S.
2021, Section 85.42, which relates to the Oklahoma
16 Central Purchasing Act; providing consequence for
certain unlawful acts; requiring certification of
17 conflict of interest compliance by state agency head;
amending 74 O.S. 2021, Section 3101, which relates to
18 newly appointed members of state agencies; requiring
ethics training for first-time state officers; and
19 adding new law 74 O.S. Section 3102.1, which relates
to conflicts of interest; stating elements of certain
20 unlawful acts; providing definitions; providing
exceptions; providing penalties; providing for
21 codification; and providing an effective date.
