1 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 344, is
2 amended to read as follows:
3 Section 344. A. Except as otherwise provided in this section,
4 every public officer, being authorized to sell or lease any
5 property, or make, approve, negotiate, or authorize any contract in
6 his or her official capacity, who voluntarily becomes interested
7 individually in such sale, lease or contract, directly or
